<Author>catuxa66
<Content>La cucaracha, la cucaracha... ya no puede caminar! Excellent location! BUT... my nephew stayed in a room infested with cockroaches. They were everywhere... on the floor, on the walls, and even in the closet. The room I stayed in was very very noisy. The balcony doors did not close all the way so you could hear the crowded street right below. The walls were so thin that we could here everything from the reception area to the people in the rooms nearby. The third room we reserved was the best room because it was on the other side of the building and not that many people were in the rooms on that side. This also happened to be the room without the bathroom. Without a doubt, the only reason that people stay at this hostel is because of it's location. 
