<Author>Krisita
<Content>Not so bad We stayed here for 3 nights,besides the bad reviews we read about this hostel, there was nowhere else to book so cheaper, near the city center and with a private bathroom.Positive aspects: great location(2 minutes from Plaza de Catalunia), price, very quiet (the street is traffic free), the room was clean and the towels changed every day.Negative aspects: the staff is not very friendly and the rooms are only to sleep, there's no tv ou telephone. So, if you want to enjoy the hotel you should probably find somewhere else, but if you only want a nice bed to sleep, in the city center and noise free, this is a good option. 
