<Author>A TripAdvisor Member
<Content>Great location at a good price Pension 45 is located on C. Tallers, 45 in the El Raval section of Barcelona, a longish block away from La Rambla (next to Hosteria Grau). They have 24-hr reception and a mix of small, private double/twin rooms, some with bath and others with a sink. The location is terrific, off the Ramblas so you don't have all the street noise (Tallers is a pedestrian lane), but close enough so you can get to the action in a 5-minute walk. The price is right too: we paid 45 euro for a double with bath, and 27 euro for a single-occupancy twin (they didn't have triples for us). The staff was really nice to us--we arrived too early for our rooms after taking an overnight bus from Bilbao, but they let us take showers in the shared bathrooms. They make you prepay for the night, and speak mostly Spanish (but are really friendly even if you don't). There is free coffee/tea in the TV lounge. The building is kind of old, but with the price as low as it is, not too shabby! 
